                <p>Knowing how to code will open more opportunities in your future.</p>
            </aside>

            <section>
                <h2>What can you do with code.</h2>
                <p>You can do so much with code. Here are my top 8 list of things you can do with code. I will discuss
                    the first two further. </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <p>1. Websites.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
